{"tid":890410,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"100公斤韓國諧星洪允花為穿婚紗「狂減30公斤」    激瘦食譜曝光","createTime":"2018-11-05T09:53:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-09T01:05:38.000Z","uid":9573,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6aee5b1028c5ae1d50181a764644f4f8ef470adf","tid":890410,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T09:53:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-11-05/656/20181105002630.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-11-05%2F656%2F20181105002630.jpg&h=11211dd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n韓國女諧星洪允花成功瘦身30公斤，勵志嫁交往8年初戀。<br />\n<br />\n韓國女諧星洪允花曾主演多部韓劇《惡作劇之吻》、《吸血鬼檢察官》、《奇蹟》，也在綜藝節目中有出色表現，本月她將與交往8年的初戀男友步上結婚禮堂，原本高達100公斤的她，努力減重30公斤，近期她公開她的減肥菜單，也讓大家感受到她的努力。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-11-05/450/20181105002636.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-11-05%2F450%2F20181105002636.jpg&h=aae24072&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n韓國諧星情侶洪允花和金民基交往8年，本月即將走上結婚禮堂。<br />\n<br />\n韓國諧星情侶洪允花和金民基在一次韓國職棒開球中，交往8年的金民基正式向洪允花求婚，當時透過直播放送轟動韓國，今年1月他們宣布將在11月舉辦婚禮，於是洪允花開始努力瘦身，日前她在IG放上瘦身前後對比照，表示自己透過運動跟調整飲食，成功減掉30公斤了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-11-05/590/20181105002643.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-11-05%2F590%2F20181105002643.jpg&h=98e31130&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n洪允花放上自己的減肥菜單，告訴大家其實減肥也能這樣吃飽飽。<br />\n<br />\n洪允花表示：「週末特別的雞肉包菜」。照片中的餐點十分豐富，有減脂增肌最佳食譜的白水煮雞胸肉、豆腐、蘑菇、青陽辣椒和洋蔥等，不但能吃到飽，卡路里還相當低。「巴基之星」今場由田泰安策騎 ，出閘時跑得頗快 ， 就連洪允花都忍不住推薦，美味又健康，也成功靠著飲食瘦下來，披上婚紗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-11-05/656/20181105002645.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-11-05%2F656%2F20181105002645.jpg&h=3da07e7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n即將在本月17日走進婚姻殿堂，兩人的好人緣屆時勢必有眾多大明星參加。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.elle.com.hk/var/ellehk/storage/images/celebrity/elle_star/tracy-chu-dec-2016-wedding-cover/capture2/21555472-1-chi-HK/Capture_img_885_590.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elle.com.hk%2Fvar%2Fellehk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Fcelebrity%2Felle_star%2Ftracy-chu-dec-2016-wedding-cover%2Fcapture2%2F21555472-1-chi-HK%2FCapture_img_885_590.jpg&h=4670d416&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n婚紗照也在日前公開，清楚看見她瘦身的成果。"},{"pid":"033005cd442a61c9b4713d500dfba9544586ab89","tid":890410,"uid":39012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T09:54:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64e339879e328979c60da6bad5048f468e81001b","tid":890410,"uid":148724,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T09:56:10.000Z","msg":"屌你 朱千雪黎wo"},{"pid":"fb3a27694b7d0d8bf7a15db252f5f9c687e230df","tid":890410,"uid":202340,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T09:57:24.000Z","msg":"「巴基之星」今場由田泰安策騎 ，出閘時跑得頗快"},{"pid":"1fb13f2a40f953de247576d0f5fb9bf46c279191","tid":890410,"uid":34561,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T09:57:41.000Z","msg":"「巴基之星」今場由田泰安策騎 ，出閘時跑得頗快 ， 就連洪允花都忍不住推薦，美味又健康"},{"pid":"733ab7b1eca06aa57cb14769a8eaf9b50b16e3c0","tid":890410,"uid":60977,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1fb13f2a40f953de247576d0f5fb9bf46c279191","tid":890410,"uid":34561,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T09:57:41.000Z","msg":"「巴基之星」今場由田泰安策騎 ，出閘時跑得頗快 ， 就連洪允花都忍不住推薦，美味又健康"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T09:59:13.000Z","msg":"呢句笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92ae5be810ee3d8b3d48d5e41735865766edef8a","tid":890410,"uid":27605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T10:01:55.000Z","msg":"都係睇到依句"},{"pid":"8331fd27eff5baf5667e80335d91bd9bb1b72b70","tid":890410,"uid":85557,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"r